d":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:54:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UiMg3GKhO3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUiMg3GKhO3g&d=pyKiqRhuC3oNCkX1YkdmvttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=e4f4dea3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UiMg3GKhO3g</a><br />\n嗰陣好多生力啤廣告都有佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a6a5f7a8f1cfc2d39bb58e865f6601b81af8dbd","tid":456480,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T05:12:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://contents.oricon.co.jp/upimg/news/20170613/2092320_201706130337436001497341566c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcontents.oricon.co.jp%2Fupimg%2Fnews%2F20170613%2F2092320_201706130337436001497341566c.jpg&h=fe598112&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/cieba70/1207730494.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fcieba70%2F1207730494.jpg&h=847e4162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實都幾型仔 你地點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7938a7167a1abd7fa137d37830616504dd294fc","tid":456480,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://stat.ameba.jp/user_images/20090518/01/tomomimaruyama/52/b4/j/t02200293_0240032010182553291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstat.ameba.jp%2Fuser_images%2F20090518%2F01%2Ftomomimaruyama%2F52%2Fb4%2Fj%2Ft02200293_0240032010182553291.jpg&h=4ac3325d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n型仔嗎😂"},{"pid":"8b8456fe544431605afed095ddf1ca1e03f668e9","tid":456480,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:56:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/18/phpMUMunj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2FphpMUMunj.jpg&h=2225f866&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依d係咪叫老年發福😂?"},{"pid":"629669b7317b4518b29cea459fe55244413c40ab","tid":456480,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"還記得「猛男孟波」嗎？ 56歲周文健現在長這樣...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/18/phpnZI5Nu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2FphpnZI5Nu.jpg&h=570c952a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n56歲港星周文健，1997年在電影《孟波》飾演男主角孟波，猛男外型加上精實肌肉，讓觀眾留下深刻印象，近年淡出演藝圈，在中國經營火鍋店，孝順的他，時常往返香港探望年邁父親。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/18/phptbtchJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F18%2FphptbtchJ.png&h=4c1e57de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1988年在《霸王花》飾演一位花心男。<br />\n<br />\n周文健接受《香港蘋果日報》訪問，聊起高齡85歲的父親周國換，透露父親一開始非常反對他去拍戲，曾號召眾親友阻止他，因父親認為，若拍戲能拍到很出名，是件很好的事，但如果名氣只是普普通通，根本很難養活家人，不如學習做生意，還比較輕鬆一些。"},{"pid":"f9723e563a32aae0171ae88feb05d46fd4fb702d","tid":456480,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T15:58:08.000Z","msg":"但周文健還是堅持進入演藝圈，1986年演出第一部電影《神探朱古力》，之後拍了啤酒廣告後，才開始收到許多電影邀約，並陸續演出《霸王花》、《八星報喜》、《逃學威龍2》、《孟波》，目前的他，已淡出演藝圈，還娶了小18歲的鋼琴老師當妻子，去年在珠海開麻辣火鍋店，身旁友人曾力勸再復出，他則表示若有適合的劇本與角色，會考慮接演。"},{"pid":"cf26a5feb390e07bacf204caa272485ecb18df34","tid":456480,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"一個已退出愚圈同一個冇人識既2打6真係冇人討論😑"}]}